    INFO: 2026-03-22 12:42:47,946:               log.py:   20: Logging to /home/user/repos/faultray/mdpdf.log
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:42:47,947:               cli.py:  103: /home/user/repos/faultray/docs/patent/faultray-patent-optimized.md
