   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:42:58,731:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |  |  Cloud API)    | Edges: Typed dependencies  |      |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:42:58,732:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |  +-----------+    +------------+---------------+      |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:42:58,733:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |                                |                      |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:42:58,734:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |                    +-----------v----------+            |
