   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:42:58,737:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |                    |  2000+ scenarios)    |            |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:42:58,738:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |                    +-----------+----------+            |
