   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:42:58,744:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |    |Engine   ||Engine   ||Engine  ||Engine ||Engine|  |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:42:58,745:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |    |(LTS)    ||(time)   ||(days)  ||(param)||(sat.)|  |
