   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:42:58,751:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |            | N-Layer Availability       |              |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:42:58,752:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |            | Constraint Model          |              |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:42:58,753:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |            | (5+ constraint layers)    |              |
