   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:42:58,757:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |            | AI Agent Cross-Layer       |              |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:42:58,758:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |            | Failure Simulation         |              |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:42:58,759:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |            | (H(a,D,I) + cascade)      |              |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:42:58,760:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |            +-------------+------------+               |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:42:58,761:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |                          v                             |
