   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:00,619:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:00,620:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:00,621:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Probabilistic
