   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:00,639:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | | Common Cause Failure Analyzer | Beta-factor correlated failure
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:00,641:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: probability |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:00,642:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:00,643:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:00,645:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Discrete/Agent-Based
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:00,647:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Discrete Event Simulation | Priority-queue event processing with exact
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:00,649:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: temporal resolution |
