   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:00,837:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Integration Pipelines
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:00,839:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Multi-Engine Consensus | Cross-engine voting and confidence
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:00,840:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: computation |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:00,841:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
