   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:06,520:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: metrics) | Formal semantics vs. static metrics; dependency types vs. uniform edges |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:06,521:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:06,530:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Availability Model | 5+
