   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:06,544:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | AI Agent Failure | H(a,D,I) as computable function of
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:06,547:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: infrastructure state | balagan-agent (real fault injection) | In-memory mathematical model vs. real-environment
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:06,548:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: observation |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:06,549:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:06,556:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Simulation Scope | Exhaustive combinatorial in-memory | Dell US11356324B2 (graph for target
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:06,557:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: selection) | Complete in-memory simulation vs. target selection for real injection |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:06,558:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:06,564:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Output | Infrastructure
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:06,566:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: modification specifications + monitoring thresholds | All prior art | Actionable remediation targeting binding
   DEBUG: 2026-03-22 12:43:06,566:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: constraints |
